US based Nigerian Comedian, Helen Paul has reacted to blogger Tunde Ednut’s post about actress Genevieve Nnaji’s alleged mental breakdown.
Genevieve has been in the public eye since she unfollowed everyone on Instagram, sparking rumours that all might not be well with her.
Concerns over her safety among fans heightened after it was rumoured that she had been admitted to a hospital in the US following an alleged mental health crisis.
Just recently, Tunde Ednut revisited the matter, saying that he hopes the actress is doing better. The blogger added that he has also unfollowed her on Instagram after finding out that Genevieve unfollowed everyone on the platform.
He wrote: “Ah ah she deleted all posts and un followed everybody ni sha. I hope she’s okay. All the best to her oo. Me sef don unfollow her.”
Comedians like Helen Paul, MC Edopikin, others stormed to the comment section to wish her well.
